If what just happened at Newark doesn’t light a fire under the FAA, what will?

Congress passed a bipartisan FAA law to fix this mess last year—more staff, better tech, safer skies.

@USDOT needs to treat this like the national emergency it is & speed up implementation now. Lives are on the the line.

The Trump Administration’s mass firings at HHS shut down five regional Head Start offices, including the one that oversees the programs in Arizona.
 
Head Start provides Arizona kids with learning programs, meals, and health care resources. Kids don’t deserve to get caught in the crossfire of these political plays.
 
@SecKennedy must reverse course.
